start server with env_variables if you like (defaults are set)

PORT,SECRET,MONGO_URL= node .

i.e.
$$ PORT=3000 SECRET=secret MONGO_URL='mongodb://localhost:27017/Cognitev_db' node .

end points:

Post /users => create new user => form-data post body

Post /users/login => login with phone_number , password => raw json post body

Post /users/validate => validate user phone_number/auth-token
